                    "spell_name": "Change Temperature",
                    "range": "0",
                    "duration": "6 turns (1 hour) + 3 turns per CA level",
                    "reversible": false,
                    "pp": 183,
                    "spell_desc": "<p>The sorcerer raises or lowers the temperature in a 10-foot radius by as much as 50\u00b0F. The caster can then move as normal, surrounded by the effect. The druidic version of this spell requires a sprig of mistletoe as a component.</p>"
                }
